metadata.name: Brothers in Contrast
metadata.description:
Brothers in Contrast, standing side by side,
Grounded by the earth beneath, separated by the space between.
Out of shadows they emerge, strong and graceful,
United yet individual, each with its own unique face.

The low mountain is broad and gentle, with curves and slopes,
A comforting presence that beckons us closer, with its open hopes.
The tall mountain, sharp and narrow, pierces the sky,
A daring challenger that inspires us to reach new heights, and to fly.

Together, these brothers remind us of the power of unity,
Of the beauty that comes from embracing diversity.
For when we stand as one, united in our differences,
We can emerge from the shadows, and rise to new brilliance.
